  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 84736f00ca5690940aa2333ea4ce800b, type: 3}
  m_Name: ThirdDream
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Her first week of being a hero broke her... She'd come back home silent, looking
    more exhausted than I'd ever seen her.
  - She'd cry when she thought I wasn't watching. I think she was afraid of ruining
    our dream. It was a wakeup call from our childhood fantasy.
  - I was the one who convinced her to quit. She tries her best to support me, but
    you can see the conflict in her eyes... I think she hates heroes.
  responses: []
